  + [prompt_text] is:
    You are performing a no-tools SOP inference job from this prompt only.
    Do not call tools, inspect files, mutate state, or claim repo authority.
    Codex owns launch, capture, validation, integration, commits, and pushes.

    Copy exactly the eight ASCII SOP lines below and output nothing else.
    Do not add commentary.
    Do not use apostrophes, curly quotes, bullets, tabs, nonbreaking spaces, or special punctuation.
    Every line after the first must begin with exactly two normal spaces, then +, then one normal space.

    & [InferenceJobResult] is task-frame routing proposal
      + [task_subject] is summarize SOP source and propose two questions
      + [lane_fit] is lm_studio proposal lane
      + [authority_boundary] is no file edits and Codex owns integration
